WEBVTT

00:05.500 --> 00:07.667
HEY.

00:09.917 --> 00:11.208
THIS ISN'T...

00:11.208 --> 00:13.375
WORKING OUT EXACTLY
THE WAY I PLANNED.

00:13.375 --> 00:16.041
