AND IT'S 65 DEGREES...

03:54.041 --> 03:57.041
ANOTHER GLORIOUS
DAY ON THE CAPE.

03:57.041 --> 03:59.375
COMING UP NEXT, AS MILLIONS
OF TEENS AROUND THE COUNTRY

03:59.375 --> 04:00.750
CRAM FOR
THIS WEEKEND'S EXAM,

04:00.750 --> 04:02.083
WE'LL TALK WITH
JOHN KATZMAN,

04:02.083 --> 04:04.083
AUTHOR OF THE BEST-SELLING
CRACKING THE PSAT.

04:04.083 --> 04:07.083
ONE STEP AHEAD OF YOU,
BABY.

04:07.083 --> 04:10.625
FOR YOUR COLLEGEBOUND
TEENAGER IN THIS MOST
COMPETITIVE YEAR EVER.

04:10.625 --> 04:12.083
COMPETITIVE, HA!

04:12.083 --> 04:13.500
TRY THIS ON FOR SIZE.

04:13.500 --> 04:16.208
DOGMATIC. SYNONYMS:
SINGLE-MINDED,

04:16.208 --> 04:16.916
STUBBORN,
OBDURATE, ADAMANT.

04:16.916 --> 04:19.416
ANTONYMS WOULD BE...

04:19.416 --> 04:21.000
WISHY-WASHY,
AMBIVALENT,

04:21.000 --> 04:26.542
UM...EQUIVOCAL.

04:26.542 --> 04:28.583
WHAT, YOU THOUGHT
THAT DAWSON WAS THE ONLY ONE

04:28.583 --> 04:30.083
WITH SUCH
A PROLIFIC VOCABULARY?

04:30.083 --> 04:32.041
NO, I JUST DIDN'T THINK
WE REALLY HAD TO STUDY

04:32.041 --> 04:34.250
WITH OUR NEWFOUND
EXTRACURRICULAR
ACTIVITIES.

04:34.250 --> 04:36.917
EASY, TIGER.
YOU HAVEN'T WON THAT
FOOTBALL SCHOLARSHIP YET.

04:36.917 --> 04:40.625
OK, YOUR TURN.
PICK A CARD, ANY CARD.

04:43.083 --> 04:45.000
NONCHALANT. OK.

04:45.000 --> 04:47.875
THE SYNONYMS WOULD BE...

04:47.875 --> 04:49.917
CAREFREE, LANGUID...

04:49.917 --> 04:52.792
OBLIVIOUS.

04:52.792 --> 04:57.834
OK, GOOD. NOW ANTONYMS.
MR. LEERY.

04:57.834 --> 04:59.458
ALERT, ATTENTIVE,
CONCERNED.

04:59.458 --> 05:02.083
THAT IS,
PROVIDED YOU BELIEVE

05:02.083 --> 05:04.125
THAT THE PSAT IS A TRUE
MEASURE OF INTELLIGENCE

05:04.125 --> 05:05.583
AND NOT A CULTURALLY-
BIASED WEAPON

05:05.583 --> 05:07.041
AGAINST THE POOR
AND DISENFRANCHISED.

05:07.041 --> 05:08.625
THAT'S A GOOD POINT,
DAWSON.

05:08.625 --> 05:11.166
STANDARDIZED TESTING
ISN'T PERFECT.

05:11.166 --> 05:13.291
IN FACT, SOME MIGHT SAY
THAT IT'S DESIGNED

05:13.291 --> 05:15.250
TO TRIP YOU UP...
MESS WITH YOUR MIND,

05:15.250 --> 05:18.333
GENERALLY CONVINCE YOU
THAT YOU'RE NOT AS SMART
AS YOU THINK YOU ARE.

05:18.333 --> 05:19.959
BUT IF YOU WANT
TO GO TO COLLEGE,

05:19.959 --> 05:21.625
IT'S THE ONLY GAME IN TOWN.

05:21.625 --> 05:23.041
[BELL RINGS]

05:23.041 --> 05:25.291
ALL RIGHT,
HANG ON, HANG ON.
NOW, LOOK, DON'T FORGET.

05:25.291 --> 05:27.250
TOMORROW:
SAMPLE MATH SECTION.

05:27.250 --> 05:30.250
OK, I NEED YOU TO BRING
A NUMBER 2 PENCIL
AND YOUR BRAINS,

05:30.250 --> 05:31.667
BOTH OF THEM SHARPENED.
THANK YOU VERY MUCH.

05:31.667 --> 05:34.625
UH, JOEY, WOULD YOU HANG ON
FOR A MOMENT, PLEASE?

05:39.834 --> 05:41.834
BELLIGERENT...

05:41.834 --> 05:43.208
UH...CRYP--

05:43.208 --> 05:44.333
OH!

05:44.333 --> 05:45.834
GOD IS NOT
THIS HUMORLESS.

05:45.834 --> 05:46.834
OW!

05:46.834 --> 05:48.792
GOD!

05:49.417 --> 05:50.583
[SIGHS]

05:50.583 --> 05:52.291
DON'T WORRY, PACEY.
THIS ISN'T GOING TO BE

05:52.291 --> 05:53.834
ONE OF THOSE
HORRIBLY AWKWARD

05:53.834 --> 05:55.500
HOPE-BOY-DIDN'T-MEAN-
ALL-THOSE-HURTFUL-THINGS-

05:55.500 --> 05:56.917
HE-SAID-DURING-THE-BREAKUP
MOMENT.

05:56.917 --> 05:58.166
WELL,
THAT'S A RELIEF,

05:58.166 --> 06:00.000
'CAUSE I SURE DON'T WANT
TO PLAY THE GUY-FEELS-GUILTY-

06:00.000 --> 06:02.041
ABOUT-BREAKUP-EVEN-THOUGH-
IT-WAS-GIRL-WHO-HAD-AN-AFFAIR-

06:02.041 --> 06:03.333
WITH-THE-MENTAL-PATIENT
SCENE.

06:03.333 --> 06:03.542
FAIR ENOUGH.

06:06.000 --> 06:08.083
NOT THAT IT'S ANY
OF MY BUSINESS ANYMORE, ANDIE,

06:08.083 --> 06:09.625
BUT HAVE YOU EVER HEARD OF
OVERPREPARING FOR A TEST?

06:09.625 --> 06:12.458
WHAT, AS OPPOSED TO
NOT PREPARING AT ALL?

06:12.458 --> 06:14.417
