TO MAKING YOURSELF CRAZY

06:14.417 --> 06:16.750
OVER SOMETHING
WITH THE WORD "PRACTICE"
IN FRONT OF IT.

06:16.750 --> 06:18.625
IF YOU WANT TO THROW
AWAY EVERYTHING WE'VE--

06:19.708 --> 06:21.333
I MEAN,
YOU'VE WORKED FOR...

06:21.333 --> 06:23.333
THAT'S FINE BY ME.

06:23.333 --> 06:24.333
HERE.

06:24.333 --> 06:26.625
ME, ON THE OTHER HAND,
I AM NOT GONNA LET

06:26.625 --> 06:27.875
OUR LITTLE BUMP
IN THE ROAD

06:27.875 --> 06:29.917
THROW ME OFF
MY CHOSEN COURSE.

06:29.917 --> 06:30.917
SEE YOU AROUND.

06:34.959 --> 06:36.625
YOU KEEP YOUR WITS
ABOUT YOU, JOEY,

06:36.625 --> 06:40.000
AND YOU GOT A LEGITIMATE
SHOT AT A NATIONAL
MERIT SCHOLARSHIP.

06:40.000 --> 06:41.125
[SIGHS]

06:41.125 --> 06:43.125
YEAH, SO EVERYONE
KEEPS TELLING ME...

06:43.125 --> 06:45.125
AND TELLING ME
AND TELLING ME.

06:45.125 --> 06:46.000
TOO MUCH PRESSURE
ON YOU, HUH?

06:46.000 --> 06:48.500
[SIGHS]

06:48.500 --> 06:49.458
I COULDN'T SLEEP AGAIN
LAST NIGHT.

06:49.458 --> 06:53.083
HMM. TRUST ME, I KNOW.
I'VE BEEN THERE.

06:54.291 --> 06:56.959
I JUST KEEP THINKING THAT
IF I DON'T ACE THIS EXAM,

06:56.959 --> 06:59.250
I'M GOING TO END UP MAKING BEDS
AND CLEANING TOILETS

06:59.250 --> 07:00.542
AT THE DEAD END MOTEL
FOR THE REST OF MY LIFE.

07:00.542 --> 07:03.583
LISTEN, HERE'S WHAT
I WANT YOU TO DO.

07:03.583 --> 07:05.000
I WANT YOU
TO TAKE THE NIGHT OFF...

07:05.000 --> 07:06.417
JUST TO RELAX.

07:06.417 --> 07:07.250
I DON'T KNOW.
HANG OUT WITH A FRIEND.

07:07.250 --> 07:09.542
RENT A MOVIE.

07:09.542 --> 07:11.375
YOU'RE GOING TO DO
JUST FINE.

07:11.375 --> 07:13.625
YOU'RE GOING TO DO
BETTER THAN FINE...

07:13.625 --> 07:16.583
AND THE FACULTY AND I
HAVE ALL THE CONFIDENCE
IN THE WORLD IN YOU.

07:19.000 --> 07:20.792
OK?

07:31.875 --> 07:33.041
DAWSON.

07:33.041 --> 07:34.083
JOEY, HI.

07:34.083 --> 07:37.000
UM, SINCE WE'VE
AGREED TO PEACE WITH HONOR,

07:37.000 --> 07:39.000
WOULD IT BE AGAINST
THE RULES OF ENGAGEMENT
TO ASK FOR YOUR HELP?

07:39.000 --> 07:41.000
OF COURSE NOT.

07:41.000 --> 07:42.625
GOOD. 'CAUSE
I COULD USE SOME.

07:42.625 --> 07:44.000
WHAT DO YOU NEED?

07:44.000 --> 07:45.208
I DON'T KNOW.

07:45.208 --> 07:46.458
A NIGHT OF MINDLESS
ENTERTAINMENT.

07:46.458 --> 07:48.625
UM, JURASSIC PARK
OR MAYBE ONE OF THOSE

07:48.625 --> 07:51.667
METEORITE-ASTEROID-
ATOMIC-BOMB MOVIES

07:51.667 --> 07:53.208
WHERE BRUCE WILLIS
OR GEORGE CLOONEY

07:53.208 --> 07:54.500
OR SOMEONE WITH
A RECEDING HAIRLINE

07:54.500 --> 07:56.041
SOMEHOW MANAGES TO SAVE
THE ENTIRE PLANET

07:56.041 --> 07:57.959
WITHOUT
BREAKING A SWEAT.

07:59.291 --> 08:01.750
I JUST NEED SOMETHING
TO TAKE MY MIND
OFF THE TEST.

08:01.750 --> 08:03.708
YEAH, YOU'VE GOT A LOT
RIDING ON IT, I KNOW.

08:03.708 --> 08:05.041
[SIGHS]

08:05.041 --> 08:07.583
JUST MY ENTIRE FUTURE.

08:07.583 --> 08:09.417
YOU TELL ME
WHEN AND WHERE.

08:10.417 --> 08:11.959
HOW ABOUT TONIGHT?

08:11.959 --> 08:13.667
TONIGHT? UM...

08:13.667 --> 08:15.083
HEY, SPORTS FANS.

08:15.083 --> 08:17.083
HOW'S 9:00?

08:17.083 --> 08:18.875
UH...

08:18.875 --> 08:20.625
UM, ACTUALLY, TONIGHT,

08:20.625 --> 08:22.875
SHE AND I WERE THINKING
THAT, UM...

08:24.166 --> 08:24.834
HEY, WHY--WHY DON'T YOU
COME WITH US?

08:28.083 --> 08:29.125
YEAH. I MIGHT, UM...

08:29.125 --> 08:31.166
ON ANOTHER PLANET,
IN A DIFFERENT UNIVERSE.

08:31.166 --> 08:33.958
NO OFFENSE.

08:36.166 --> 08:37.833
HA. WHAT WAS THAT ABOUT?

08:43.166 --> 08:45.792
I'D APPRECIATE
SOME CONTACT, PEOPLE!

08:45.792 --> 08:48.250
COME OFF THE GROUND HARD
AND POP, POP!

08:48.250 --> 08:48.959
PUT SOME HURT ON!

08:48.959 --> 08:51.000
EXECUTE!

08:52.166 --> 08:54.083
YOU'RE UP, McPHEE.

08:55.625 --> 08:57.875
ALL RIGHT, JACK,
YOU CAN DO THIS.

08:57.875 --> 08:59.708
NOW, JUST REMEMBER,
WHEN YOU'RE HIT,

08:59.708 --> 09:00.834
BUTTON UP,
BECOME FETAL.

09:00.834 --> 09:03.375
HUG THAT BALL.
HUG THAT BALL!

09:03.375 --> 09:04.291
HUG THAT BALL.

09:04.291 --> 09:07.041
HUG THAT BALL.

09:07.458 --> 09:09.041
[WHISTLE]

09:09.041 --> 09:10.792
Teammate:
TAKE IT TO HIM.

09:15.750 --> 09:18.208
