09:18.208 --> 09:21.208
HOW TO HIT, BABY!
HOW TO HIT!

09:21.208 --> 09:24.667
GET UP, McPHEE.
YOU'RE DEFACING
THE LANDSCAPE.

09:24.667 --> 09:26.458
AGAIN.

09:26.458 --> 09:28.208
COME ON, COACH.
CAN'T YOU SEE WHAT'S
GOIN' ON HERE?

09:28.208 --> 09:29.208
