09:29.208 --> 09:30.041
YEAH, BUT NOT
FOR THE REASONS YOU THINK.

09:30.041 --> 09:32.000
GIVE ME A BREAK.
IT'S OBVIOUS.

09:32.000 --> 09:33.375
LOOK, JACK,
GAY OR STRAIGHT,

09:33.375 --> 09:35.041
YOU ARE STILL
THE NEW KID ON THE BLOCK,

09:35.041 --> 09:37.250
AND YOU ARE NOT
PROTECTING THE FOOTBALL
THE WAY THAT YOU SHOULD.

09:37.250 --> 09:38.834
NOW DO IT AGAIN.

09:42.000 --> 09:43.375
McPHEE!

09:43.375 --> 09:45.708
3-POINT STANCE!

09:47.708 --> 09:47.750
[WHISTLE]

10:05.375 --> 10:05.750
[WHISTLE BLOWS]

10:07.583 --> 10:08.583
CAN YOU HEAR ME,
JACK?

10:08.583 --> 10:11.667
JACK, YOU KNOW
WHERE YOU ARE?

10:11.667 --> 10:13.083
HOW MANY FINGERS?

10:14.083 --> 10:14.792
I THINK I'M GONNA HURL.

10:22.583 --> 10:24.083
I MEAN, THIS GUY'S
NOT EXACTLY

10:24.083 --> 10:25.917
WHAT YOU WOULD CALL
A LADIES' MAN. HEH.

10:25.917 --> 10:27.083
BUT I TELL HIM.
IT IS EASY.

10:27.083 --> 10:29.792
THERE'S ONLY ONE RULE,
PLAIN AND SIMPLE:

10:29.792 --> 10:33.375
GIVE THE LADIES
WHAT THEY WANT.

10:34.333 --> 10:36.750
HOW ABOUT GIVING ME
WHAT I WANT, ROB?

10:36.750 --> 10:38.834
