10:42.625 --> 10:44.708
YEAH, SURE.
WHY NOT? NO SWEAT.

10:44.708 --> 10:46.417
I REMEMBER
WHAT IT WAS LIKE.

10:46.417 --> 10:48.458
OF COURSE, I DIDN'T
TAKE THE PSATs.

10:48.458 --> 10:49.458
WHAT, DADDY BUILT
THE UNIVERSITY?

10:49.458 --> 10:51.750
NO, NO.
JUST ENDOWED IT.

10:51.750 --> 10:54.083
ACTUALLY,
I HIRED A RINGER.

10:55.291 --> 10:56.750
SERIOUSLY.
PAID SOME BRAINIAC

10:56.750 --> 10:58.458
