11:05.458 --> 11:08.291
I OWE YOU ONE.

11:08.291 --> 11:09.750
WELL, UH,
HERE'S A THOUGHT.

11:09.750 --> 11:12.667
YOU LET ME TAKE YOU OUT
FOR A POST-PSAT
CELEBRATION.

11:12.667 --> 11:16.125
SATURDAY NIGHT.
YOU AND ME.

11:16.125 --> 11:18.542
UH, THANKS, BUT, UM...

11:18.542 --> 11:20.834
