LIKE ME SEEING OTHER PEOPLE.

11:20.834 --> 11:24.333
OH, SURE. THOUGHT YOU
WERE GONNA SAY YOU
HAD TO WASH YOUR HAIR.

11:24.333 --> 11:25.708
NO, THAT'S WEDNESDAYS.

11:25.708 --> 11:28.834
ACTUALLY, ROB,
THE TRUTH IS...

11:28.834 --> 11:30.083
I'M A LESBIAN.

11:30.083 --> 11:30.667
OH...

11:30.667 --> 11:32.667
ANYONE I KNOW?

11:33.834 --> 11:35.000
SO, IS IT A DATE?

11:35.000 --> 11:36.625
