IF I JUST SAID NO?

11:40.458 --> 11:43.834
YEAH.
SURE THING, POTTER.

11:43.834 --> 11:45.792
NO PROBLEM.

12:09.417 --> 12:12.291
[CHUCKLES]

12:12.291 --> 12:14.542
