TO WORRY ABOUT YOU.

12:15.542 --> 12:17.959
I WAS SEARCHING
FOR THE PERFECT APPLE.

12:17.959 --> 12:20.208
GO AHEAD.
TAKE A BITE.

12:20.208 --> 12:22.625
SEE IF IT TASTES
AS GOOD AS IT LOOKS.

12:23.375 --> 12:24.875
AND IF I DO?

12:24.875 --> 12:27.625
YOU WILL FOREVER
KNOW THE DIFFERENCE
BETWEEN GOOD AND EVIL.

12:28.625 --> 12:31.000
GET OUT HERE, DAWSON.

12:31.000 --> 12:33.667
IT'S A BEAUTIFUL NIGHT.

12:42.708 --> 12:43.750
[SIGHS]

12:43.750 --> 12:46.083
WELL, I HAVEN'T
BEEN OUT HERE SINCE...

12:46.083 --> 12:46.458
SINCE JOEY AND I WERE--

12:46.458 --> 12:48.166
JOEY?

12:48.166 --> 12:50.834
YOU MEAN
THE UBIQUITOUS
BRUNETTE?

12:50.834 --> 12:52.458
THE ONE WHO
HASN'T YET LEARNED

12:52.458 --> 12:54.000
THE POWER AND SWAY
SHE HOLDS OVER
THE HEARTS OF MEN?

